description	"Padme Amidala

Class: Hero.
Class Summary: 
A medic (Heals Armor) and commander that carries a powerful blaster. 

Weapons:
- E-5 Blaster (Based on A280 level 1)
- Concussion Grenade (1)
- Fire Grenade (1)

Inventory:
- Bacta (+25 HP)
- Large Bacta (+50 HP)

Attributes:
- Rally

Abilities:
- Can recover allies' armor (Press the 'Use' key while adjacent and facing teammate with depleted armor)
- Can view ally stats
- Dodge (2) [Class Special 1]

Padme Amidala was a human female senator who represented the people of Naboo during the final years of the Galactic Republic. Prior to her career in the Galactic Senate, Amidala was the elected ruler of the Royal House of Naboo. A political idealist, she advocated for the preservation of democracy as well as a peaceful resolution to the Clone Wars."